com.tomscz.afswinx.component.skin

Class BaseSkin

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomscz.afswinx.component.skin.BaseSkin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Skin
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MySkin

    public class BaseSkin
extends java.lang.Object
implements Skin
    This is default implementation of Skin interface. It should be also used as default skin if no skin is created and set by user. Extends from this class if you want to make you skin or implement Skin interface.
    Since:
    1.0.0.
    Author:
    Martin Tomasek (martin@toms-cz.com)
